---
layout: layout.njk
title: Skills 分类
navSection: skills
description: 按分类浏览 Agent Skills，便于开发者快速找到所需能力。
permalink: categories/index.html
---

<script>document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() { window.location.replace("/#/skills"); });</script>
<section class="skills-zaobao-layout" aria-hidden="true">
  <aside class="skills-left">
    <div class="skills-left-row">
      <div class="skills-category-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="分类">
        {% for parent in skillsIndex.categoryTreeWithCounts %}
        <a href="/categories/{{ parent.slug }}/" class="skills-category-tab {% if loop.first %}is-active{% endif %}" role="tab">{{ parent.nameZh or parent.name }}</a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="skills-children-wrap">
        {% set firstParent = skillsIndex.categoryTreeWithCounts[0] %}
        <ul class="skills-children-list">
          {% for child in firstParent.children %}
          <li>
            <a href="/categories/{{ child.fullSlug }}/" class="skills-child-link">{{ child.nameZh or child.name }}</a>
          </li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>
  <div class="skills-content">
    <h1 class="skills-page-title">按分类浏览</h1>
    <p class="skills-page-desc">按使用场景浏览技能，便于快速找到所需能力。同一技能可能属于多个分类。请从左侧选择分类。</p>
  </div>
</section>
